        <abstract> 
<p>John Murray has announced his next book [<hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>] without CD’s knowledge. It is only half-written. JVC will hear when it is published and will decide whether it is worth translating. It will be dry, but, CD believes, of value.</p> 
            <p>Has read an account of JVC’s Scottish lectures.</p>
            <p>Invites JVC to Down.</p>
        </abstract>
